&lt;p&gt;Famous last words from a software engineer. I said them with confidence during my MCP dataclass debugging session. I had this vivid memory of calling the function with a dataclass parameter and watching it work in production.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then I did the git archaeology. It never worked. Not once. The memory was completely false.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;






 
 
